ខ្ញុំ...

00:15:20.950 --> 00:15:21.740
Xiao Qianqing!

00:15:30.640 --> 00:15:32.050
ខ្ញុំនឹងវិនាសជាមួយអ្នក!

00:15:32.070 --> 00:15:32.740
Xiao Qianqing!

00:15:32.920 --> 00:15:33.770
Xiao Qianqing!

